name: Unpainted Lion Air 737-800 Go Around at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, today's video is a short one; a Lion Air 737-800 doing a go-around at Paine Field. My first go-around video! I was pretty surprised when I heard his engines spooling up and saw him pitch up :) I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
